title: Mercenary Support looking for Crash team
body:
Won some sort of Crash Beta Cup last time in a Tier 4 team with 4 other gold players. Seems like they have quit this game though, so looking for new team.

[Crash Game History #2](https://matchhistory.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-details/OC1/210122055/201025528?tab=overview)
